vegetarian /ˌvɛdʒɪˈtɛərɪən/

(vegetarians) 

1. ADJ Someone who is vegetarian never eats meat or fish. 素食的 

例： Yasmin sticks to a strict vegetarian diet. 亚斯敏坚持一种严格的纯素饮食。 

2. N-COUNT A vegetarian is someone who is vegetarian. 素食者 

例： ...a special menu for vegetarians. …一份针对素食者的特殊菜单。 

3. ADJ Vegetarian food does not contain any meat or fish. 素的 

例： ...vegetarian lasagnes. …素意式宽面条。

